HEADWORD: Intently
<hw>In*tent"ly</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>adv.</pos> <def>In an intent
manner; <as>as, the eyes <ex>intently</ex> fixed</as>.</def></p>

<p><syn><b>Syn.</b> -- Fixedly; steadfastly; earnestly; attentively;
sedulously; diligently; eagerly.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Intentness</ent>⟦br⟧
